'''Infobox game''' - Template for game information boxes.

==Usage==

<pre>
{{Infobox game
| title = Game Title
| alt_title = Alternate Title (optional)
| image = Image filename.jpg
| developer = Developer Name
| publisher = Publisher Name
| platform = NES/SNES/GBA
| release = Release date(s)
| genre = Game genre
| players = Number of players
| mapper = ROM mapper type
| rom_size = ROM size
| ram_size = RAM/SRAM size
}}
</pre>

==Parameters==

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| title || Yes || Game title
|-
| alt_title || No || Alternative title (regional variants)
|-
| image || No || Box art image filename
|-
| developer || Yes || Development company
|-
| publisher || Yes || Publishing company
|-
| platform || Yes || Console platform
|-
| release || Yes || Release date(s)
|-
| genre || Yes || Game genre
|-
| players || No || Number of players
|-
| mapper || No || ROM mapper/memory controller
|-
| rom_size || No || ROM size
|-
| ram_size || No || Work/Save RAM size
|}

==Example Output==

{{Infobox game
| title = Dragon Warrior IV
| developer = Chunsoft
| publisher = Enix
| platform = NES
| release = February 11, 1990
| genre = RPG
| players = 1
| mapper = MMC5
| rom_size = 1 MB
| ram_size = 8 KB
}}

